{Speech 2}{}{You’re in the wrong tavern, ain’t ya?@@We don’t need troublemakers here.@@[Mumble, mumble] ...sorry ass outa town...@@Head west to Trapper Town, if you want a place to sack out later..@@Another one of Dunton’s gang.@@[Looks at you and then shakes his head]@@[Makes a subtly rude gesture]@@You better not steal our brahmin...@@No room for the likes of you.@@Just keep moving.}
{Speech 3}{}{What are you looking at?@@Buy us all a round of drinks, newcomer...@@Hope you can hold your liquor.@@You don’t look like a cannibal.@@Too many strangers lately.@@Well, at least your teeth ain’t filed into points.@@We’re keeping an eye on you.@@Buy us a round of drinks!@@Hi!@@Don’t go wandering at night.@@If your anxious, try the Bathhouse.@@If you’re smart, you’ll stay away from the Duntons.@@Got me a good trapline south of here.}
{Speech 4}{}{Welcome, friend.@@Hope you like our city.@@Klamath is the place to be.@@Nice to have you here.@@[Raises his mug to you]@@[Winks at you]@@Nice to see someone new in town.}
{Speech 5}{}{There goes the neighborhood.@@Weather’s getting ready to turn, I guess...@@Jist as long as you don’t get too much firewater in you...@@Trapping’s good lately.@@It looks deserving my attention.@@I thought you'd never ask. Nothing like Buckner’s Best.@@Rather have a bottle in front of me...}
{Speech 6}{}{Ok.@@Thanks.@@Mmm-mm.@@Thanks for the brew.@@Huzzah!@@Thank you.@@Thanks, friend.@@I sure needed that. Thanks.@@Thanks a million!@@Much obliged, friend.@@Alright!@@Yes! I was waiting for that.@@Thanks, friend.@@Thanks.@@Yeah!}
